  <div class="post" id="post-257">
    
    <div class="nextprev">
      <div class="alignleft">&laquo; <a href="http://blog.linkedin.com/2007/07/19/linkedin-for-go/" rel="prev">Grameen Foundation does LinkedIn&nbsp;for Good</a></div>
      <div class="alignright"><a href="http://blog.linkedin.com/2007/07/27/antarctica-2007/" rel="next">Antarctica 2007: Swimming&nbsp;with the Penguins!</a> &raquo;</div>
