As a Healthcare Executive Coach, I plan on referring my clients to your blog, your words, and your advice.  I found it very easy to read and incredibly complete. Way to go!  You have provided a very good service to our networks and the public, especially those of us who really want to increase the effectiveness of LinkedIn as a personal and business tool.</p>
<p>Keep up the great work!</p>
<p>Rod Meyer, CPC<br />
Pleasanton, CA</p>

